000Z","msg":"Dllm cls"},{"pid":"66d32b186fbfa84ec134bb6aa791fad6cd296574","tid":1536591,"uid":124455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f6825c93f6689eec7f6b66023c5593832dca23","tid":1536591,"uid":99738,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"English version: <br />\n<br />\nwe, hong kongers, are facing another humanitarian crisis today. A young protestor was attacked by the police at Prince Edward MTR flatform in 3 September evening. According to a first aider who was at the scene, the boy vomitted, suffered neck pain, GCS:3/15, pulse kept dropping, breath was shortening that he required a 100% conc oxygen mask... these signs suggested he was suffering from a cord injury. The closer the injured part is to the head/neck region, the higher chance he would die due to the shut down of involuntary ventilation. Even in less severe case, he might be paralysed. <br />\n<br />\nYet, at this critical moment, the police stopped him from receiving proper medical treatment! The suitation was beyond urgent, and required immediate help from a licensed medical personell, some might need to be accessed to the ICU for a projection of airway.<br />\n<br />\nThe clock was ticking and he gradually entered a state of deep coma. The first aider begged the police to ease the boy's handcuffs, which held his hands at hjs back, since they would only further worsen the boy's injuries. Police not only rejected his request, they even dragged the boy's unconscious body around, until the ambulance finally arrived after 30 mins. <br />\n<br />\nThe boy's current state remains unknown, yet the police's misconduct and their ignorance is totally unacceptable."},{"pid":"92138ded68c758b633f978253450c2c60e5b773e","tid":1536591,"uid":279637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:03:04.000Z","msg":"毋忘831"},{"pid":"a4a5e0f90ec59b7eaa357824a6871fd1fa7dcf96","tid":1536591,"uid":74586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:04:26.000Z","msg":"我地唔好再得把口<br />\n我都好驚，但對住呢班狗，我地唔可以再怕，我地一齊打狗，一齊升級好嗎<br />\n<br />\n我地一齊以來既升級只有打爛啲死物，但佢地就不斷合理化佢既武力，仲一直向我地既頭部攻擊甚至恐襲。下次，再有啲狗追人，我地企硬唔好再走了。應承手足，呢一世都唔好原諒班狗，好嗎"},{"pid":"541aa083cf6aa2ac0883071c46c1b95571a8fa77","tid":1536591,"uid":33319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:06:11.000Z","msg":"黑警還命"},{"pid":"d9616eda93cacda5652c2c36a70c9b73332c3c48","tid":1536591,"uid":250610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bd082936d3035a4cc1e37dd4ff004ed474a7f158","tid":1536591,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d71c284d48121ffb5ff2e0d6f1a941e23e46fdb1","tid":1536591,"uid":64126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:06:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香<br />\n港<br />\n警<br />\n察<br />\n<br />\n蓄<br />\n意<br />\n謀<br />\n殺</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"c9ad78227baa91378b4ef10700386676da3fcb2b","tid":1536591,"uid":64126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:07:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香<br />\n港<br />\n警<br />\n察<br />\n<br />\n蓄<br />\n意<br />\n謀<br />\n殺</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"d0fceabfc05991ac129efba77943bb1fba2e3821","tid":1536591,"uid":64126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:07:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香<br />\n港<br />\n警<br />\n察<br />\n<br />\n蓄<br />\n意<